Daily Trust


Six people have been reportedly kidnapped on Kaduna-Abuja expressway.They were said to be from Offa and were abducted at Rejana along theKaduna-Abuja Expressway on Sunday.The spokesman for the Offa Descendants’ Union, Maruf OlalekanAjenifuja, in a statement, said the victims were travelling with AdukeOkin Motors from Offa to Kaduna.“This worrisome incident happened at Rejana along the Abuja-Kadunaexpressway thereby throwing many families into a period of sorrow.“ODU has waded in and efforts are in top gear to secure the release ofthe victims and we hope they would be released soonest by the specialgrace of God."We may not be able to give you details at the moment due to securityreasons,” he said.